        p
          | A. Scholup provides quality home tuition. We provide tutors who come to your home and help your child build a strong foundation in various subjects.
        p.question
          | 2. What is so special about Scholup? There are competing home tuition bureaus in the market.
        p
          | A. A tuition bureau’s job is finished after providing you with a tutor.  We manage the student’s whole syllabus providing practice worksheets and test along with the tuition. In the unlikely event of a tutor leaving, he is replaced within 2-3 working days. The new tutor will start from where the previous tutor left. As opposed to in the case of tuition bureau where you have to search the new tutor and explain the new teacher about completed course.
